xt":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27953,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/20\/allah-opens-door-argument-action\/","url_meta":{"origin":38042,"position":3},"title":"Ma&#8217;ruf on Arguing: If Allah guides him, he acts and does not argue","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Ma\u2019ruf al-Karkhi, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf Allah wills goodness for a servant, He opens the door of action and closes the door of disputation. If Allah wills harm for a servant, He closes the door of action and opens the door of disputation.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39789,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/19\/conscience-admonish\/","url_meta":{"origin":38042,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Conscience: Allah makes his heart admonish him with good","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen Allah intends goodness for a servant, He appoints a conscience within him to command and prohibit him.\u201d Source: Zahr al-Firdaws 227 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to al-\u2018Iraqi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u0651\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\